name: Bose Sleepbuds II - True wireless earphones - in-ear - Bluetooth - noise isolating | Dell USA
description: Everyday stress. Snoring. Noisy neighbors. There's plenty that keeps you awake. Introducing Sleepbuds II. Tiny and comfortable, Sleepbuds work with the Bose Sleep app to deliver relaxing sounds to help you fall asleep, and use Bose noise-masking technology so you stay asleep all night.
